Term
-----

Term Rewriting library based on the Free monad representation of terms.

Providing, for any representation of terms, generic
 - matching
 - unification
 - equality up to renaming
 - rewriting
 - innermost rewriting (work in progress)
 - narrowing
 - basic narrowing
 - narrowing on demand

author: Pepe Iborra
maintainer: pepeiborra@gmail.com
homepage: http://github.com/pepeiborra/term

